Whether it is daily wear or travel, it can become the shining point of girls. A stylish bag for girls 3-9 years old. (The plush fabric uses tie-dye technology, color is random)

🎁Perfect Gift for Girls: This doll-unicorn themed gift is not only a gift, but also a good wish for your little girl’s growth and happiness. This is the perfect gift to bring surprise and joy into your little princess's life! Whether it's her birthday, Christmas, back-to-school gift, or holiday celebration, this unique gift will create wonderful memories for her.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute doll carrier
reviews.reviewText: This is a really convenient and cute doll carrier. The carrier is really nice for transporting and storing the doll away. The accessories are durable and add more playability to this play set. The colors are pretty and the carrier and doll seem to be holding up quite well to my little one’s daily play. Really cute way to carry her doll around and see her at the same time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lovely small doll
reviews.reviewText: My 4 year old daughter loves dolls, and this will make a great addition to her set. It’s small so it fits in well, and easy to manage. The small backpack the doll is encased in is cute, feels soft, and colorful so it’s appealing to toddlers. I recommend this as a gift for a niece or daughter.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Fun carry case
reviews.reviewText: This doll is a cute little one to carry around. The doll itself is only 6" but that makes it a fun size. However, being so small, the clothes are a little difficult to get on and off so it might be tedious for a 3-year-old. For our 5yo, it is still tough, but she is up to the challenge and hopefully her dexterity will improve. As for the stars that are supposed to appear on the face at 0 degrees, I couldn't make that happen. I put her in the freezer which is set a -2, so that should have done the job. That wasn't so important to me, just don't make it a selling point for your little one.
